        "       EV&f of a &ePokémon&f by &a1&f if you",
        "     Right-click it. The item is consumed",
        "                    Upon use."
    ],
    "quest.0D93842A83F0F91E.quest_subtitle": "Speed EV",
    "quest.0E0CB3B3FF94B180.quest_desc": [
        "        A &cBurn Heal&f is a type of",
        "     Medicine used to heal the burn",
        "           Status of a &ePokémon&f."
    ],
    "quest.0E0CB3B3FF94B180.quest_subtitle": "Burn",
    "quest.0E1E4DD2581225AC.quest_desc": [
        "              The &bIcy Rock&f is a",
        "            Held &eItem&f that boosts",
        "",
        "        The duration of &bHail&f weather",
        "            To a total of &e8 turns&f."
    ],
    "quest.0E1E4DD2581225AC.quest_subtitle": "Extends the duration of Hail to 8 turns",
    "quest.0E429E02C6EA28B8.quest_subtitle": "Plasma Armor",
    "quest.0EAA6D03C1954519.quest_subtitle": "Anorith",
    "quest.0EEA18BB01524FBE.quest_desc": [
        "     A &bMega Stone&f is a type of held    ",
        " Item that lets a &ePokémon&f &dMega Evolve&f  ",
        "                   In battle.                ",
        "",
        "    Each &dMega Evolution&f requires a ",
        "    Different &bMega Stone&f to be used. ",
        "",
        "   A &bMega Stone&f can be obtained by",
        "                Defeating a ",
        "       &6Mega Evolved boss&f &ePokémon&f.",
        "   Which will drop its corresponding",
        " ",
        "                &bMega Stone&f.",
        "   If the &bMega Stone&f has not already",
        "  Been obtained before, it will always",
        " Drop. Otherwise, it has a 1\/40 chance.",
        "",
        " A &ePokémon&f can &dMega Evolve&f only if it",
        " Holds its matching &bMega Stone&f and if",
        "The holder is wearing a &9Mega Bracelet&f. ",
        "",
        " In battle, a &bMega Stone&f is not affected ",
        " By &amoves&f that remove held items, such   ",
        "        As Trick, Knock Off, Embargo, ",
        "                  Magic Room."
    ],
    "quest.0EEA18BB01524FBE.quest_subtitle": "How do mega stones work?",
    "quest.0F2D359C0433887B.quest_subtitle": "&aSpeed &8\/ &cAttack",
    "quest.0F8700B15331C2E5.quest_desc": [
        "        In the &echapters &fyou will find",
