    "quest.110D90B64DFF7B17.quest_subtitle": "Axe",
    "quest.1145B4274729072A.quest_desc": [
        "          The &9Quick Powder&f is a",
        "            Held &eItem&f of speed.",
        "",
        "      It doubles &dDitto&f's &bSpeed&f stat,",
        "     But only when not &cTransformed&f.",
