    "quest.11A30167D830479C.quest_subtitle": "Water Axe",
    "quest.11B84239BE238567.quest_desc": [
        "             The &2Dusk Ball&f is a",
        "         Special type of &bPoké Ball&f",
        "",
        "   It has a &e3× Catch Rate&f in dark or",
        "            Nighttime locations.",
        "",
        "    In &dNether&f and &5End&f dimensions, it",
        "      Always counts as &7Night&f time.",
        "",
        "   Conditions for boosted effect:",
        "  &7•&f Pokémon below height level &e64&f",
        "  &7•&f Light level &e14&f or lower",
        "  &7•&f Rain in sunlight triggers effect",
        "",
        "    &7Snow in sunlight does not trigger",
        "    The boosted effect of Dusk Ball.",
        "",
        "    Against &5Ultra Beasts&f it only has",
        "             A &c0.1× Catch Rate&f."
