    "quest.13560B0CB5903DC8.quest_subtitle": "Time for good",
    "quest.135AB8A1CF56912B.quest_desc": [
        "       An &aorb&f of &bfrozen souls&f is      ",
        "   An item that can be used to spawn   ",
        "                   &bArticuno&f.              ",
        "",
        "To do so, the &aorb&f needs to be charged ",
        "   By defeating &6375&f &dPokémon&f with the  ",
        " &aOrb&f in the player's inventory and then ",
        "        Used on a frozen &cshrine&f.       ",
        "",
        " The &dPokémon&f do not have to be &3Ice&f or",
        "            &9Water&f-type &dPokémon&f.        ",
        "",
        " The remaining number of &dPokémon&f to    ",
        "  Defeat can be displayed by using the",
        "                     &aOrb&f."
    ],
    "quest.135AB8A1CF56912B.quest_subtitle": "Articuno",
    "quest.1384BB3848B5DF98.quest_subtitle": "Sun Sword",
    "quest.13CF3A3C861E5068.quest_desc": [
        "      A &bWater Stone&f is an evolution",
        "   Stone that can be obtained through",
        "        Crafting, fishing, and more.",
        "",
        "    &bWater Stone&f can be used for the",
