        "          &6Staryu &f→ &6Starmie",
        "          &6Eevee &f→ &6Vaporeon",
        "          &6Lombre &f→ &6Ludicolo",
        "          &6Panpour &f→ &6Simipour",
        "          &6Hisuian Qwilfish &f→ &6Overqwil."
    ],
