    "quest.13EDFC4AC6882804.quest_subtitle": "Moon Stone",
    "quest.143C291573661076.quest_desc": [
        "    The &aHealth Feather&f is a type of",
        "   Medicine that increases the &cHP EV&f",
        "        Of a &ePokémon&f by &a1&f if you",
        "     Right-click it, consuming the item",
