    "quest.14BC70DE98A071FD.quest_subtitle": "Fairy-Type",
    "quest.14F133692E1A15B5.quest_desc": [
        "             The &aSport Ball&f is a",
        "          Special type of &bPoké Ball&f",
        "",
        "     It has a &e1.5× Catch Rate&f on wild",
