        "          Turning into &bPorygon2&f."
    ],
    "quest.2E5438CB6D246970.quest_subtitle": "Porygon -> Porygon2",
    "quest.2E62E31788E1F99D.quest_desc": [
        "           The &7Metal Powder&f is a",
        "            Held &eItem&f of defense.",
        "",
        "      It raises &dDefense&f and &dSp. Def&f",
        "           Of &dDitto&f by &e+50%&f total,",
        "     But only when not &cTransformed&f.",
        "",
