    "quest.31292A5F23DF929E.quest_subtitle": "More standard than the poke ball",
    "quest.312FE91A3D9328F8.quest_subtitle": "Mega Evolution Pokemon",
    "quest.313C82CEF255DD51.quest_desc": [
        "    The &cMuscle Feather&f is a type of",
        "   Medicine that increases the &cAttack",
        "       EV&f of a &ePokémon&f by &a1&f if you",
        "     Right-click it, consuming the item",
