    "quest.322E261EE66C4D9B.quest_subtitle": "Mega Evolution Stone",
    "quest.32396FCE65518A3C.quest_desc": [
        "        A &6Full Restore&f is a type of",
        "    Medicine used to fully restore the",
        "       HP of a &ePokémon&f and heal all",
