        "       Survive a fatal hit with &c1 HP&f,",
        "   Then is consumed upon being used.",
        "   Does not prevent fainting from own",
        "   Explosion, Healing Wish, Memento, or",
        "                 Selfdestruct."
    ],
    "quest.32C37C95065F6EB8.quest_subtitle": "Lets the holder survive a fatal hit with 1 HP if it is at full HP",
    "quest.33367BC6132C41E0.quest_desc": [
        "        A &eStatic Shrine&f is a shrine      ",
        "    That spawns rarely in &6Savanna&f",
        "                    Biomes.                    ",
        "",
        " If a fully-charged &aOrb of Static Souls&f ",
        "   Is placed in its centerpiece, the       ",
        "     &dLegendary&f &eZapdos&f will spawn.    ."
    ],
    "quest.33367BC6132C41E0.quest_subtitle": "Electric bird",
    "quest.337D3EB57FE7BCE7.quest_subtitle": "Mega Evolution Pokemon",
    "quest.338537EE5A58E455.quest_subtitle": "Mega Evolution Stone",
    "quest.342E4F41CA282B51.quest_desc": [
        "       A &9Dragon Fang&f is a held item.",
        "    It boosts &9Dragon&f moves' power by",
        "                &a20%&f when held."
    ],
    "quest.342E4F41CA282B51.quest_subtitle": "Boosts Dragon-type moves",
    "quest.34A23EB85BAA4020.quest_desc": [
        "      A &6Power Belt&f is a power item.",
        "  When held, &ePokémon&f gain normal EVs",
        "    Plus &a+8 Defense EVs&f after battle.",
        "      The holder's &bSpeed&f is halved.",
