        "                Transform:",
        "",
        "    Any &5Ghost-Type&f move that isn't a",
        "   Status move becomes the fierce",
        "    &dNever-Ending Nightmare&f attack.",
        "",
        "     &cEmbargo&f, &cKlutz&f or &cTrick&f cannot",
