        "          &6Floette &f→ &6Florges."
    ],
    "quest.35C3EB1686DDBDA6.quest_subtitle": "Shiny type?",
    "quest.36381D1B8A2DEF37.quest_desc": [
        "        The &dPsychium Z&f is a unique",
        " &eZ-Crystal&f for &dPsychic-Type Pokémon&f.",
        "",
