        "",
        "       Moves this &eZ-Crystal&f can",
        "                Transform:",
        "",
        "     &6Clanging Scales&f becomes the",
        "    &dClangorous Soulblaze&f attack.",
        "",
        "     &7Special:&f Only a &6Kommo-o&f can",
        "                Use this move.",
        "",
        "     &cEmbargo&f, &cKlutz&f or &cTrick&f cannot",
