    "quest.47726C6AE65B1DB3.quest_subtitle": "Steel-Type",
    "quest.478589B527F911C8.quest_subtitle": "Moon Axe",
    "quest.479D20CA5EAE3ED8.quest_desc": [
        " After obtaining the &cRed Chain&f and the",
        "       &6Legendary Orb&f, you may now",
        "             Activate the &aAltar&f.    ",
        "",
        "   First, right-click the &aAltar&f with the   ",
        "  &cRed Chain&f, which will change its color",
        "   And start particle effects in front.",
        "",
        "  Next, right-click with the chosen &6Orb&f",
        "               On the &aAltar&f.              ",
        "",
        "After a short animation, the &dLegendary&f",
        "     Will rise from the ground and",
        "  The player if they have a &bPokémon&f ",
        "            That is Not fainted. ",
        "",
        "   If the player chooses to flee, the",
        "        &dLegendary&f will disappear.         ",
        "",
        "    If the player has no unfainted ",
        "                  &bPokémon&f,",
        " The &dLegendary&f will roam around until",
        "              It is challenged.             "
    ],
    "quest.479D20CA5EAE3ED8.quest_subtitle": "Palkia, Dialga, Giratina",
    "quest.47A60507C6FEB5A1.quest_subtitle": "Craft",
    "quest.47AE58ADE0C19760.quest_desc": [
        "            &cBreed your Pokémon",
