        "    Medicine that temporarily raises a",
        "      &ePokémon's&f &dSpecial Attack&f by one",
        "             Stage while in battle."
    ],
    "quest.4CCFAAC1711F97F2.quest_subtitle": "Sp. Attack",
    "quest.4CE3134BE655C378.quest_desc": [
