    "quest.4CFCE711671F7D9F.quest_subtitle": "??????????",
    "quest.4D6426F667C03950.quest_desc": [
        "        An &bAwakening&f is a type of",
        "    Medicine used to remove the sleep",
        "         Status from a &ePokémon&f."
    ],
    "quest.4D6426F667C03950.quest_subtitle": "Sleep",
    "quest.4D930F8432681276.quest_desc": [
        "              The &fShell Bell&f is a",
        "             Held &eItem&f of healing.",
        "",
        "     It restores &c1\/8 HP&f to the holder",
        "      From the direct damage it deals",
