        "  Make a &aPokémon&f drop the &eZ-Crystal&f",
        "                 It is holding."
    ],
    "quest.4FDEF1B27C5D0C5A.quest_subtitle": "Bug-Type",
    "quest.5060DC7728DCD2FE.quest_desc": [
        "            To be able to craft",
        "             &6Ancient Poké Balls&f",
        "     You need to find these &dStones&f",
        "",
        "        They can be obtained by",
        "       Mining &eTumblestone Crystals&f",
        "              With a hammer.",
        "",
        "      Found in &aMountainous&f biomes,",
        "      But most abundant within the",
        "    &dUltra Plant&f biome in &5Ultra Space&f",
        "",
        "                      Or",
        "",
        "             By killing &aPokémon&f",
        "             The chance is &e10%&f",
        "",
        "           &7Bastiodon&f      &eBonsly&f",
        "           &7Cranidos&f       &5Drapion&f",
        "           &7Onix&f             &7Rampardos&f",
        "           &7Rhydon&f         &7Rhyhorn&f",
        "           &7Rhyperior&f     &7Shieldon&f",
        "           &5Skorupi&f        &eSudowoodo&f."
