    "quest.50E70B1AD0B7E237.quest_subtitle": "Paralyze",
    "quest.511EF5A01FE6AA4C.quest_desc": [
        "            The &7Ring Target&f is a",
        "           Held &eItem&f of strategy.",
        "",
        "      It negates &bType Immunities&f on",
        "            Its holder in battle.",
        "",
