    "quest.511EF5A01FE6AA4C.quest_subtitle": "Negates type immunities on the holder",
    "quest.51362842C45C0843.quest_subtitle": "Plasma Armor",
    "quest.51382824AA0B000D.quest_subtitle": "Mega Evolution Pokemon",
    "quest.519A59FE83BC968F.quest_desc": [
        "               Need I speak?",
        "",
        "    A &dRare Candy&f is an item that can",
        " Level up a &ePokémon&f. &dRare Candies&f can",
        "  Be obtained as a tier &a1 special drop&f,",
        "  As a drop from boss &ePokémon&f, or in",
        "              Max Raid Battles.",
        "",
        "        Using a &dRare Candy&f on a",
        "              &ePokémon&f owned",
        " By the player will consume it and raise",
        "        Its level by &a+1&f instantly.",
        "",
        "       While holding a &dRare Candy&f",
        "                 Nearby wild",
        "  &ePokémon&f will follow the player — and",
        "   Owned ones will follow more closely.",
        "",
        " Even when max leveled, a &dRare Candy&f",
        " Can still be used to evolve a &ePokémon&f."
    ],
    "quest.519A59FE83BC968F.quest_subtitle": "Serious?",
    "quest.51A30B066CA934F6.quest_desc": [
        "               Hello Trainer!",
        "       I know the path is difficult",
        "   But I'll teach you a little something",
        "",
        "    Did you know that your Pokémon",
        "          Can be &ahealed &fduring",
        "              Their battles?",
        "",
        "          That's right my friend",
        "        Take it easy, I'll help you",
        "",
        "       Not just healing, There are",
        "    Several things that will help you."
    ],
