        "            A turn if it is in battle."
    ],
    "quest.5B1670540D9200A5.quest_subtitle": "Burns the holder at the end of a turn during battle",
    "quest.5B68982B15DE23D6.quest_desc": [
        "     The &7Silver Bottle Cap&f is an item",
        "  That increases one of the six stats",
        "    (HP, &cAttack&f, &9Defense&f, &dSp. Attack&f,",
        "     &dSp. Defense&f, and &bSpeed&f) of a",
        "    Max level &ePokémon&f to act as if",
        "           It had a perfect &aIV&f.",
        "",
        "    When you right-click a max level",
        "     &ePokémon&f with it, you can select",
        "     What stat you want to increase.",
        "",
        "  &7Silver Bottle Caps&f are obtainable",
        "    Via fishing, as a drop from 3–5★",
        " Max Raid Battles and as a tier 3 or 4",
        "                 Special drop.",
        "",
        " Bottle Caps only affect the &aIVs&f for",
        "  Battling purposes. It doesn't affect",
        "  The type of Hidden Power nor affect",
        "                   Breeding."
    ],
    "quest.5B68982B15DE23D6.quest_subtitle": "It's too op",
    "quest.5B841B6375AC9A0F.quest_subtitle": "Thunder Shovel",
    "quest.5BA4925AEC17A560.quest_desc": [
