        "        Instantly engaged in battle",
        "",
        "  To spawn a regular &dCelebi&f you must",
        "  Right-click the &aShrine&f with a &6GS Ball&f.",
        "",
        "   To obtain an &5Alien Celebi&f you must",
        "  Capture a &dCelebi&f inside a &9Beast Ball&f.  ",
        "",
        "     To spawn a &eSpiky-Eared Pichu&f",
        "          You need a &ePichu&f with ",
        "         Maximum friendship and    ",
        "  Use forage on the &aIlex Shrine&f while",
        "    Having a free slot in your &bparty&f."
