    "quest.6F207D775B43CF05.quest_subtitle": "Extends the duration of Light Screen, Reflect, and Aurora Veil to 8 turns",
    "quest.6F29EFD22DAD2892.quest_subtitle": "&aSpecial Attack &8\/ &cSpecial Defense",
    "quest.6F6AAEEAC2E8CD9E.quest_subtitle": "Fire Armor",
    "quest.6FCE42BD9483D77D.quest_subtitle": "Team armor",
    "quest.701E6FA4AF9486F0.quest_desc": [
        "       An &dExp. Share&f is a held item.",
        "    It gives &aEXP&f to the holder even if",
        "    It does not battle, as long as the",
        "     &ePokémon&f is not fainted and is in",
        "                 The party.",
        "",
        "    If it does not battle, it gains &a50%&f",
        " Of EXP and all EVs from the foe. If it",
        "    Battles, it gains the full amounts.",
        "",
        "  Multiple &dExp. Shares&f do not conflict;",
        "  All holders receive the full effects."
    ],
    "quest.701E6FA4AF9486F0.quest_subtitle": "Share EXP",
    "quest.70361F1EE29F4295.quest_subtitle": "Hammer or Hammer",
    "quest.704B9CC491E63654.quest_desc": [
        "        The &aOrb&f of &bFiery Souls&f is      ",
        "   An item that can be used to spawn   ",
        "                  &eMoltres&f.              ",
        "",
        "To do so, the &aOrb&f needs to be charged",
        "   By defeating &6375&f &dPokémon&f with the  ",
        "   &aOrb&f in the player's inventory and   ",
        "      Then used on a &cFiery Shrine&f.    ",
        "",
        "  The &dPokémon&f defeated do not have",
        "       To be &cFire&f-type &dPokémon&f. ",
        "             ",
        " The remaining number of &dPokémon&f to",
        "  Defeat can be displayed by using the",
        "                      &aOrb&f."
